scene.message:
Nanjo: She's usually{nl}
irritating, but having Ayase{nl}
around at a time like this is{nl}
somehow a relief.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: The same scenery no{nl}
matter how far we go...{waitkey}Are we really making{nl}
progress, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

???: Oh, hello. Nice to meet{nl}
you.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm Mariko Yabe, of the{nl}
Yamagumo Private High School{nl}
Paranormal Phenomena Club.{waitkey}Pleased to meet you!{waitkey}{clearbox}Though it's an unofficial club{nl}
where I'm both president and{nl}
sole member, ha!{waitkey}{clearbox}My homeroom teacher won't{nl}
approve the club, for the sole{nl}
reason that it's "uncool"!{waitkey}{clearbox}So today I came to meet my{nl}
comrade Kuroori, but...{nl}
little{wait_fr:30}... little{wait_fr:30}... did I...{waitkey}{clearbox}did I dream I'd get caught up{nl}
in a paranormal event this{nl}
amazing! I'm super lucky!{waitkey}{clearbox}Until just now I was exploring{nl}
the three mysterious towers{nl}
that appeared around school!{waitkey}{clearbox}The towers are full of demons!{nl}
Thanks to that, I got loads{nl}
of great photos!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'm gonna submit those demon{nl}
photos to a magazine!{waitkey}{clearbox}If the media takes notice,{nl}
maybe my teacher will approve{nl}
the club!{waitkey}All right! I'll give it{nl}
my all!{waitkey}{ret}

Mariko: I'd pretty much{nl}
finished exploring the{nl}
towers, so I climbed up{nl}
here, but...{waitkey}I'm a little tired, I admit...{waitkey}{clearbox}But this situation gets me{nl}
fired up! "The school's{nl}
mysterious freeze"! "The{nl}
demons' revival"!{waitkey}"The mystery towers and the{nl}
school turned labyrinth"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Say, what do you think?{waitkey}{clearbox}I still think it's the plot{nl}
of a secret society scheming{nl}
to rule the world through{nl}
magic...{waitkey}{ret}
